Thinking quickly, Teltoli reverted to her Fuzor Panther/Hawk beast 
mode, and the shot whizzed over her head. Taking a few running steps 
and a leap with the liquid movement of a big cat, aimed her curved 
fangs towards his throat, leaping from a bare meter away.
